result.notes:
Organogram (organisation chart) showing all staff roles. Names and salaries are also listed for the Senior Civil Servants 2* and above.

Organogram data has been released by all central government departments and their agencies since 2010. Snapshots for 31st March; 30th June; 30th September and 31st December are published each year. The published data is validated and released in CSV format and OGL-licensed for reuse. For more information about this series, see: http://guidance.data.gov.uk/organogram-data.html
